data.description: This home has so much to offer! With a little TLC, you can make this home your own.  This two story home has 4 bedrooms upstairs with 2 full bathrooms. The Flex space upstairs would make a great office or play room. The downstairs has the living room-kitchen combo, a separate dining area, half bath, indoor laundry room and an extra family room which could be utilized for so many things. If you are looking for space, you will want to see this home. New roof was installed in 2021. This quiet neighborhood is close to The Villages and all the local amenities. Come check it out for yourself!
